beer.beer_description:
Inspired by the wild spirit of the Yeti, our latest craft beer is made with a unique blend of premium ingredients, including Voyager Veloria Malt, rolled oats, Voyager Winter Wheat, Simpsons Caramalt Malt, and a blend of orange hops featuring Amarillo, Citra, and Mosaic.
This beer is characterized by its clean and smooth bitterness and a blast of citrus flavour that will transport your senses to a tropical paradise. You'll notice the aroma of a blend of orange and tropical fruits with a subtle hint of blood orange and white grapefruit.

The Wild Citrus IPA is the epitome of untamed flavour, and it's sure to unleash the inner beast in you. So, get ready to experience a beer that's truly wild and full of flavour.
